Installation
------------

Installing prerequisites on ubuntu::

    $ sudo apt-get install build-essential python-dev

To install the synapse module run::

    $ python setup.py install

To setup a development version run::

    $ python setup.py develop

To run the tests run::

    $ python setup.py test

Basic Usage
-----------

To run a home server::

    $ python -m synapse.app.homeserver

Or::

    $ synapse-homeserver

For a complete list of parameters run::
    
    $ synapse-homeserver -h

Building Documentation
----------------------

Before building documentation install spinx and sphinxcontrib-napoleon::

    $ pip install sphinx
    $ pip install sphinxcontrib-napoleon

Building documentation::

    $ python setup.py build_sphinx
